			<p>
				No one telling you where to go, what to do, or where to stay.
			</p>
			<p class="bg-yellow-200 w-fit mt-4">Plan your trip like you always do.</p>
			
			<p class="bg-yellow-200 w-fit font-semibold">Then watch it come to life on RunwayHorse.</p>
		</section>
		<%= image_tag "marketing/home.png", class: "shadow-xl max-w-5xl h-auto mx-auto mt-12" %>
